title: Monkey House (1991) 7 Vonnegut Stories Len Cariou
description:
This oddity was produced in Vancouver a quarter century ago. These 25 minute renditions of seven of Kurt Vonnegut's short stories bring out his ironic sense.(However, "Welcome to the Monkey House" is not among them). I mentioned Len Cariou because I admired his performance in Sweeney Todd.

The Foster Portfolio
All the King's Men (starring Len Cariou).
Next Door 
More Stately Mansions
Fortitude
The Euphio Question
Epicac (lacking the last 3 minutes).
